Summer Membership
Atlantic National Golf Club
Summer Membership Program
May 3rd – October 31, 2025
Registration is
CLOSED
for new Summer Members
Summer Membership Benefits Include:
5
Discounted Greens Fees for duration of Summer Membership
5
10 FREE Small buckets of range balls (valued at $90.00)
Redeemable only at registration facility. Once all 10 buckets are used, they will be available at a discounted price of $5.00 to Summer Members.
5
10 Day Advance Tee Time Reservation Access
5
BONUS: First 500 registrants receive an ANGC Hat!
**Membership is non-refundable and non-transferable**
Regular Summer Golf Rates:
$53.00 on Weekdays, $64.00 on weekends and Holidays before 12pm
ANGC Summer Member Rates Valid 5/3 – 10/31/25:
Monday-Friday:
$36.45 before 10:30am
$29.91 after 10:30am
$23.36 after 2:30pm
Saturday, Sunday, and Holidays:
$45.79 before 11:00am
$36.45 after 11:00am
$28.04 after 2:30pm
(Above fees do not include sales tax. Rates are subject to change)
*Membership is non-refundable & non-transferable*
